-- Swiss Banking Group Surveys U.S. Client Deposits, Le Matin Says
-- B y   D e r m o t   D o h e r t y
-- 2012-04-08T10:07:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-08/swiss-banking-group-surveys-u-s-client-deposits-le-matin-says.html
The  Swiss Bankers Association  is
carrying out a survey of banks to determine the extent of
deposits by U.S. clients,  Le Matin Dimanche  reported, citing a
spokeswoman for the association.  Such information is necessary to conclude an agreement with
the U.S., the newspaper reported, citing Rebeca Garcia.  To contact the reporter on this story:
